metadata.name: TORQUESQUAD Future Racer Livery
metadata.description:
The first official collaboration piece between Torquesquad and Paperlegend. 

This Livery design was made for one of the original hand-drawn Characters ( by IAN GALVIN). This piece is the "foundation" of an ongoing collaboration.

This NFT is accompanied by a physical sculpture in scale 1:8 and will be shipped to the first buyer.

The [1/1 sneak peek](https://www.instagram.com/p/CbQMd6PP4Hj/) was posted on the 18th of March 2022.
